{"tid":1219185,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"屬於香港人嘅城邦歌","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:18:50.000Z","uid":184771,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5923e756bbea5b513884364c607f540d19d17a2a","tid":1219185,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"城邦歌就似區旗，代表香港。<br />\n香港現時民意主要有和理非民主派、勇武民主派<br />\n呢首歌，要適合所有屆別，旋律要用西洋正樂作曲，並預備管弦樂及合唱團的編曲，莊重嚴肅。歌詞激昂並簡而精表達香港特色同歷史。兼且，屌鳩7婆呢個賣港賊！！<br />\n<br />\n推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PErttjfrv1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPErttjfrv1I&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADUZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=f02a6307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PErttjfrv1I</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong>皇皇香港，育我長我地方。歷劫不動城邦。<br />\n華英並茂，古今交集，流芳百世有我承當。<br />\n九七風霜，淪落蠻荒，美好家園一朝喪！<br />\n同道奮起，鐵馬金戈，摧碎離地賣國奸賊黨！<br />\n刀劍伸張，光芒萬丈，妖魔驅逐不許還鄉。<br />\n修我水土，築我門牆，國土千秋萬世永無疆。<br />\n復我河山，攜我少長，四海縱橫大國邦。</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n此歌詞的第一句皇皇、育我，來自《詩經》。第二句歷劫不動，來自佛法，城邦來自古希臘。最後一句，來自岳飛還我河山，王羲之《蘭亭集序》少長雲集。四海縱橫是呼應香港歷來的海濱城市對外闖蕩的格局，即是香港遠洋貿易、捕魚及海盜的傳統。"},{"pid":"18d58c5e85b17efbb84bd849fec8622fbe6dbff1","tid":1219185,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb729d2e2cae08e2a0d47ce028899cf5f2816be0","tid":1219185,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18d58c5e85b17efbb84bd849fec8622fbe6dbff1","tid":1219185,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"集思廣益！推推推！"},{"pid":"5dc4a45edfd304f65546e092598c5b8ab5c2694e","tid":1219185,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc